<template lang="pug">
.song-list
   ul(v-for="(song, id) in playlist")
    li index: {{ id}}
    li videoId: {{ song.videoId }}
    li name: {{ song.name }}
</template>
<script>
import { usePlaylistStore } from '../store/playlist'
export default {
  data() {
    return {
      playlist: []
    }
  },
  mounted() {
    this.loadPlaylist()
  },
  methods: {
    loadPlaylist() {
      const playlistStore = usePlaylistStore()
      this.playlist = playlistStore.getFirstPlaylist

    }
  }
}
</script>

<style></style>
